# PDAL Conversion to COPC

This repo has samples for how to use python to convert PDAL (.las) files to COPC format. It uses the pdal-python libraries and has samples for Linux, Docker and AWS Lambda deployments.

# Deployment Types

## Linux

The pdal_linux folder includes a install_bash.sh file that includes the installation procedures for installing the pdal libraries via conda.

## Docker

The pdal_docker folder includes a install.sh file that includes the installation procedures for building, testing and deploying the docker repo to AWS Fargate.

## AWS Lambda

the pdal_docker_lambda folder inclues a install.sh file that includes the installation procedures for building, testing and deploying the docker image to AWS lambda for invocation.

## AWS Batch

the pdal_docker_batch folder includes a install.sh file that includes the installation procedures for building, testing and deploying the docker image to AWS Lambda for invocation from S3 Batch Operations
